column4: Bough down before me. I'm your local tree, {spc_common}.
Every day is arbor day when you're an NYC Street Tree.
Good things come in trees, like me, {spc_common}.
Hug me, but don't hang on me, I'm a {spc_common}.
See me. Love me. Hug me. I'm your tree, {spc_common}.
I don't feel well. Come visit.
{spc_common} is my name. I'm all over this town.
